text: Akaki Minashvili (; born 24 September 1980) is a Georgian politician. He was a member of the Parliament of Georgia from 2008 to 2012, from 2012 to 2016 and from 2020. == Other websites == *Biographical entry on the website of Georgia's parliament Category:1980 births Category:Members of the Parliament of Georgia Category:Politicians from Tbilisi Category:Living people
title: Akaki Minashvili
